title: WalkScore of 86/100, On-Site Laundry Facilities
posting_body: ['Carlisle on the Park Apartments', '995 Humboldt St, Denver, CO, 80218', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 61', 'OR Text', '61', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Welcome to Carlisle on the Park!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 755 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'If you are looking for some of the most versatile, pet-friendly apartments for rent Capitol Hill, Denver has to offer with a prime location in a highly walkable neighborhood, you have come to the right place - Carlisle on the Park.', 'Our recently remodeled one- and two-bedroom apartments provide a spacious layout to call your own.', 'With features like two-tone paint, a full appliance package, crown molding, and mirrored closet doors, our homes find the right balance of comfort and style.', 'You will appreciate community conveniences that include on-site laundry facilities, a fitness center, and off-street reserved parking.', 'Pet Policy', 'We love your pets and are excited to welcome them to their new home!', 'We allow two pets per apartment home with a combined weight not exceed 160 lbs.', 'Cats and dogs are welcome at our community although some breed restrictions apply.', 'Pet Deposit for 1 Pet: $100', 'Pet Fee for 1 Pet: $300', 'Monthly Pet Rent for 1 Pet: $35', 'Pet Deposit for 2 Pets: $200', 'Pet Fee for 2 Pets: $500', 'Monthly Pet Rent for 2 Pets: $65', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'cJH4dVfuElnL']
